{"root":{"data":{"text":"科研论五步法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lvykg7bp40","created":1738898181424,"text":"搜"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw298va2w0","created":1738898470492,"text":"方法：构造检索式"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw2bmijmo0","created":1738898475671,"text":"步骤："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw3em30gg0","created":1738898560539,"text":"（1）百度、必应、wiki等搜索关键词，了解基本概念"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7m95kw24f40","created":1738935405360,"text":"对于多个单词组成的词组（没有词条），可结合其他关键词一起搜索，从文献宣传报道中找到相关文献"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw3hnbydc0","created":1738898567145,"text":"（2）CNKI学术翻译寻找关键词对应英文及同义词"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7m9g25e9uo0","created":1738936226572,"text":"缺陷：根据翻译或背景知识来获取英文表达容易遗漏一些同义表达，从而导致搜索时遗漏文献"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw3k30aeo0","created":1738898572447,"text":"（3）构造表达式使用文献搜索引擎（WoS、Scopus等 ）搜索，测试"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7mxmojue1k0","created":1739004452157,"text":"删除测试"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw3m60jog0","created":1738898576982,"text":"（4）标题检索判断检索词及其之间逻辑关系设置正确后，检索范围可扩大到主题（topic）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw3ozkbb40","created":1738898583122,"text":"常见情况"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw48858u80","created":1738898625000,"text":"案例1：两/多个检索词单独检索结果多，但合并检索结果少"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw4b565fs0","created":1738898631350,"text":"情况1：相对较新的研究领域（寻找idea的方法）","progress":9},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw5axywtk0","created":1738898709279,"text":"情况2：两个概念本身没太大关联"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw5grgcvs0","created":1738898721946,"text":"案例2：同义词过多，难以确定"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw5j631j40","created":1738898727184,"text":"解决方法：检索式精简，less is more"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw5l1yy600","created":1738898731289,"text":"带来的问题：引入不相关结果"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw5nfohg00","created":1738898736471,"text":"Think out of box，不直接相关的研究可以带来许多启发和思考（寻找idea的方法）","progress":9},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw5pzfoqw0","created":1738898742020,"text":"使用“鲸吞法”解决"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7m3uggma1s0","created":1738920428164,"text":"通过精简检索式搜索后，可了解相关同义表达"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw5xhjt6w0","created":1738898758352,"text":"案例3："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw9anyxvc0","created":1738899022131,"text":"词组关键词拆分，获得最小单元"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7m9kltmtyw0","created":1738936582853,"text":"解决方法：第一步通过网络搜索确定最小单元，通过搜索到的相关文献确定相关的英文表达并记录；第二步使用学术词典类软件获取其他可能的同类表达"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw95vnsc00","created":1738899011712,"text":"案例4："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw9b8lzrs0","created":1738899023379,"text":"Branch topics"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw9burhe80","created":1738899024719,"text":"案例 5："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw9g8v4ps0","created":1738899034279,"text":"Branch topics"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw9gp8hsw0","created":1738899035268,"text":"案例6："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw9jesu3k0","created":1738899041168,"text":"Branch topics"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw9n2iybs0","created":1738899049133,"text":"案例7："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw9q5pyco0","created":1738899055856,"text":"Branch topics"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw9r1x0bk0","created":1738899057803,"text":"案例8："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d7lw9tvfme80","created":1738899063941,"text":"Branch topics"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw1y46n2o0","created":1738898446264,"text":"聚"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw209h9zc0","created":1738898450938,"text":"分"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw21d6on40","created":1738898453339,"text":"验"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d7lw22gwv1s0","created":1738898455741,"text":"合"},"children":[]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-purple-compat","version":"1.4.43"}